  "description": "A lighter evening recipe designed to feel comforting without becoming heavy or starch-dense. Coconut Vegetable Soup with Ragi String Hoppers brings a distinct structure, seasoning pattern, and grain-legume balance to the table.",
  "preparation": "",
  "cooking_steps": [
    "Warm a pot on medium heat with oil. Add onion, ginger, chilli, and curry leaves and soften for 2 minutes without browning.",
    "Add the vegetable, peas, salt, and 180 ml water. Cover and cook on medium-low heat for 6 minutes until just tender.",
    "Add coconut milk and simmer gently on low heat for 4 minutes until lightly thickened.",
    "Serve the hot stew over the idiyappam so the strands absorb flavor but still retain shape."
  ],
